{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/swift_Tuple/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"swift의-tuple\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#swift%EC%9D%98-tuple\" aria-label=\"swift의 tuple permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Swift의 Tuple</h3>\n<p>먼저 Tuple은 Collection Type이 아니다. Collection Type에는 Array, Dictionary, Set만이 있다. 그래도 Type이긴 하다.</p>\n<p>Tuple은 구조체와 비슷하다.\n<code class=\"language-text\">var tuple = (1, &quot;Hello, world!&quot;, true)</code>\n이런식으로 여러가지 타입을 한꺼번에 묶어서 사용할 수 있다.</p>\n<p>여기서 Tuple도 타입이기 때문에 Tuple안에 Tuple도 가능하다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"tuple-사용방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tuple-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"tuple 사용방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tuple 사용방법</h3>\n<p>실제로 다른 컬렉션 타입이나 구조체 때문에 Tuple을 쓸 일은 거의 없다. </br>\n그래도 사용방법에 대해 알아보자.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> tuple <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Hello, world!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\ntuple<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span>    <span class=\"token comment\">// 1</span>\ntuple<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span>    <span class=\"token comment\">// \"Hello, world!\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이런식으로 인덱스만 찍어주면 바로 값에 접근이 가능하다.</p>\n<p>또 다른 사용법으로 '이름'을 주는 방식이다.\n<code class=\"language-text\">var namedTuple = (name: &quot;Zedd&quot;, age: 999, likes : [Swift, iOS])</code></p>\n<h5 id=\"생긴게-딕셔너리와-비슷한듯\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%83%9D%EA%B8%B4%EA%B2%8C-%EB%94%95%EC%85%94%EB%84%88%EB%A6%AC%EC%99%80-%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%B7%ED%95%9C%EB%93%AF\" aria-label=\"생긴게 딕셔너리와 비슷한듯 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>생긴게 딕셔너리와 비슷한듯..</h5>\n<p>이렇게 선언하면 인덱스 대신 이름을 찍어줄 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> namedTuple <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Jito\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> age<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">999</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> likes <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token builtin\">Swift</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> iOS<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nnamedTuple<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name    <span class=\"token comment\">// \"Jito\"</span>\nnamedTuple<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>age     <span class=\"token comment\">// 999</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>나름 쓸모 있어 보이는 튜플이지만 Swift 문서에 따르면, </br></p>\n<h3 id=\"tuples-are-useful-for-temporary-groups-of-related-values--if-your-data-structure-is-likely-to-persist-beyond-a-temporary-scope-model-it-as-a-class-or-structure-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tuples-are-useful-for-temporary-groups-of-related-values--if-your-data-structure-is-likely-to-persist-beyond-a-temporary-scope-model-it-as-a-class-or-structure-\" aria-label=\"tuples are useful for temporary groups of related values  if your data structure is likely to persist beyond a temporary scope model it as a class or structure  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tuples are useful for temporary groups of related values. (…) If your data structure is likely to persist beyond a temporary scope, model it as a class or structure (…)</h3>\n<h3 id=\"튜플은-관련된-값들을-임시로-그룹지을때-유용합니다--만약-데이터구조가-임시범위를-넘어서-존속할-가능성이-있는-경우에는-클래스나-구조체로-모델링하십시오\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%9C%ED%94%8C%EC%9D%80-%EA%B4%80%EB%A0%A8%EB%90%9C-%EA%B0%92%EB%93%A4%EC%9D%84-%EC%9E%84%EC%8B%9C%EB%A1%9C-%EA%B7%B8%EB%A3%B9%EC%A7%80%EC%9D%84%EB%95%8C-%EC%9C%A0%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%A9%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4--%EB%A7%8C%EC%95%BD-%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0%EA%B0%80-%EC%9E%84%EC%8B%9C%EB%B2%94%EC%9C%84%EB%A5%BC-%EB%84%98%EC%96%B4%EC%84%9C-%EC%A1%B4%EC%86%8D%ED%95%A0-%EA%B0%80%EB%8A%A5%EC%84%B1%EC%9D%B4-%EC%9E%88%EB%8A%94-%EA%B2%BD%EC%9A%B0%EC%97%90%EB%8A%94-%ED%81%B4%EB%9E%98%EC%8A%A4%EB%82%98-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0%EC%B2%B4%EB%A1%9C-%EB%AA%A8%EB%8D%B8%EB%A7%81%ED%95%98%EC%8B%AD%EC%8B%9C%EC%98%A4\" aria-label=\"튜플은 관련된 값들을 임시로 그룹지을때 유용합니다  만약 데이터구조가 임시범위를 넘어서 존속할 가능성이 있는 경우에는 클래스나 구조체로 모델링하십시오 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>튜플은 관련된 값들을 임시로 그룹지을때 유용합니다 (...) 만약 데이터구조가 임시범위를 넘어서 존속할 가능성이 있는 경우에는 클래스나 구조체로 모델링하십시오.</h3>\n<p>라고 한다.</p>\n<p>본 포스팅은 <a href=\"https://zeddios.tistory.com/238\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://zeddios.tistory.com/238</a> [ZeddiOS] 를 참고했습니다.</p>","excerpt":"Swift의 Tuple 먼저 Tuple은 Collection Type이 아니다. Collection Type에는 Array, Dictionary, Set만이 있다. 그래도 Type이긴 하다. Tuple은 구조체와 비슷하다.\n\n이런식으로 여러가지 타입…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/swift_Tuple/#swift%EC%9D%98-tuple\">Swift의 Tuple</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/swift_Tuple/#tuple-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\">Tuple 사용방법</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/swift_Tuple/#tuples-are-useful-for-temporary-groups-of-related-values--if-your-data-structure-is-likely-to-persist-beyond-a-temporary-scope-model-it-as-a-class-or-structure-\">Tuples are useful for temporary groups of related values. (…) If your data structure is likely to persist beyond a temporary scope, model it as a class or structure (…)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/swift_Tuple/#%ED%8A%9C%ED%94%8C%EC%9D%80-%EA%B4%80%EB%A0%A8%EB%90%9C-%EA%B0%92%EB%93%A4%EC%9D%84-%EC%9E%84%EC%8B%9C%EB%A1%9C-%EA%B7%B8%EB%A3%B9%EC%A7%80%EC%9D%84%EB%95%8C-%EC%9C%A0%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%A9%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4--%EB%A7%8C%EC%95%BD-%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0%EA%B0%80-%EC%9E%84%EC%8B%9C%EB%B2%94%EC%9C%84%EB%A5%BC-%EB%84%98%EC%96%B4%EC%84%9C-%EC%A1%B4%EC%86%8D%ED%95%A0-%EA%B0%80%EB%8A%A5%EC%84%B1%EC%9D%B4-%EC%9E%88%EB%8A%94-%EA%B2%BD%EC%9A%B0%EC%97%90%EB%8A%94-%ED%81%B4%EB%9E%98%EC%8A%A4%EB%82%98-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0%EC%B2%B4%EB%A1%9C-%EB%AA%A8%EB%8D%B8%EB%A7%81%ED%95%98%EC%8B%AD%EC%8B%9C%EC%98%A4\">튜플은 관련된 값들을 임시로 그룹지을때 유용합니다 (...) 만약 데이터구조가 임시범위를 넘어서 존속할 가능성이 있는 경우에는 클래스나 구조체로 모델링하십시오.</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/swift_Tuple/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Swift Tuple","date":"Apr 22, 2021","tags":["Swift"],"keywords":["MojitoBar","Ju dongseok"],"update":"Apr 22, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/swift_Tuple/","series":[],"lastmod":"2021-04-22"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2027115977","694178885"]}